 月 5 日星期六在伦敦芬斯伯里公园举行</a>。这将是他们迄今为止最大的头条表演，并得到了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/amyl-and-the-sniffers">Amyl And The Sniffer</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kneecap">Kneecap 的</a>支持。 </p><figure id="attachment_3786762" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3786762" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3786762" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Reading24_NME_AFORD_FONTAINESDC-69476.jpg" alt="方丹特区 2024 年雷丁节。图片来源：Andy Ford / NME" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Reading24_NME_AFORD_FONTAINESDC-69476.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Reading24_NME_AFORD_FONTAINESDC-69476-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Reading24_NME_AFORD_FONTAINESDC-69476-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Reading24_NME_AFORD_FONTAINESDC-69476-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Reading24_NME_AFORD_FONTAINESDC-69476-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Reading24_NME_AFORD_FONTAINESDC-69476-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3786762" class="wp-caption-text"> Fontaines DC 出席 2024 年雷丁节。图片来源：Andy Ford / NME</figcaption></figure><p>不久之后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-d-c-announce-massive-2025-manchester-show-at-wythenshawe-park-3797642">他们将于8月15日前往曼彻斯特的威森肖公园</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/english-teacher">英语老师</a>和Kneecap将再次与他们会合。室外场馆总容量为26,000名球迷，门票已于本月初开始发售。</p><p>今年夏天早些时候，《Romance》问世，标志着他们的第四张专辑，也是新厂牌 XL Recordings 的第一张专辑。 <em>《NME》</em>在对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/James-Ford">詹姆斯·福特</a>制作的唱片给予<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/fontaines-d-c-romance-review-3784445">五星级好评</a>时表示：“《浪漫》提供了奇妙而严肃的时刻，同时也偶尔让人感到不祥的预感。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" id="324854070" title="与 Fontaines D.C. 的 Grian Chatten 相处融洽：“我们的个性比我们发出的声音更重要”" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/cAncWquXDE8?start=268&amp;enablejsapi=1#038;feature=oembed" width="100%" height="392" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" data-gtm-yt-inspected-6="true" data-mce-fragment="1"></iframe></p><p>对于专辑的方向， <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/fontaines-d-c-grian-chatten-interview-at-home-romance-favourite-new-album-3784142">乐队告诉<em>NME，</em>他们希望摆脱</a>首张专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/fontaines-dc-dogrel-album-review-2474751">Dogrel</a> 》中摇滚的声音。</p><p> “被太多人创造性地理解就像苍蝇落在你的衣服和脸上。时不时地，你必须他妈的摆脱它们，才能再次看到你是谁。这就是我们想做的，”他说。</p><p>该乐队最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/elton-john-fontaines-d-c-are-the-best-band-out-there-at-the-moment-3795882">被埃尔顿·约翰誉为“目前最好的乐队”</a> ，并于本周早些时候<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-d-c-announce-2025-japan-australia-and-new-zealand-tour-dates-3805334">宣布了日本、澳大利亚和新西兰的新巡演日期。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-d-c-announce-2025-us-headline-tour-3807704">Fontaines DC 宣布 2025 年美国巡回演唱会的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
得益于档案录音，克里斯托弗·李在新的《指环王》电影中回归饰演萨鲁曼https://www.nme.com/news/film/christopher-lee-back-as-saruman-in-new-lord-of-the-rings-film-thanks-to-archival-recordings-3807679?utm_source= rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=克里斯托弗·李在新《指环王》电影中饰演萨鲁曼，感谢档案录音Emma WilkesTue, 29 Oct 2024 22:04:54 +0000Film News https://www.nme.com/?p=3807679 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/christopher-lee-mike-marsland-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="克里斯托弗·李" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/christopher-lee-mike-marsland-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/christopher-lee-mike-marsland-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/christopher-lee-mike-marsland-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/christopher-lee-mike-marsland-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/christopher-lee-mike-marsland-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/christopher-lee-mike-marsland-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>第一部动漫《指环王》电影将于 12 月上映</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/christopher-lee-back-as-saruman-in-new-lord-of-the-rings-film-thanks-to-archival-recordings-3807679">克里斯托弗·李 (Christopher Lee) 在新的《指环王》电影中回归饰演萨鲁曼 (Saruman) 的消息得益于档案录音，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/christopher-lee-mike-marsland-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="克里斯托弗·李" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/christopher-lee-mike-marsland-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/christopher-lee-mike-marsland-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/christopher-lee-mike-marsland-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-con