ujatniK/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" style=" color:#c9c8cd; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; line-height:17px; text-decoration:none;" target="_blank">EUROVISION NEWS (@esc_news_) 分享的帖子</a></p></div></blockquote><p><script async src="//platform.instagram.com/en_US/embeds.js"></script></p><p></p><p>今年早些时候，前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/years-years">Years &amp; Years</a>歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olly-alexander">Olly Alexander</a>在比赛中演唱了歌曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olly-alexander-shares-new-solo-single-and-eurovision-entry-dizzy-3595340">“Dizzy”</a> ，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olly-alexander-truly-grateful-for-eurovision-support-calls-getting-zero-points-iconic-3756355">在 25 个国家/地区中获得了第 18 名</a>。陪审团只给他打了 46 分，但公众投票却没有给他打分。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sweden-win-eurovision-song-contest-2023-as-uk-finishes-second-from-last-3443082">梅·穆勒 (Mae Muller) 在去年演唱了歌曲《我写了一首歌》后，在 2023 年获得了倒数第二名</a>，在此之前，英国队也在 2021 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/james-newman-says-hell-focus-on-the-positives-after-nil-points-at-eurovision-2947452">获得了零分</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/uk-did-worse-than-thought-at-eurovision-song-contest-2019-2491410">在 2019 年排名垫底</a>。</p><p>在此之前， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-react-as-uk-come-second-to-ukraine-at-eurovision-2022-sam-ryder-kalush-orchestra-3225813">莱德在 2022 年为英国取得了近期记忆中最令人印象深刻的成绩</a>——位居第二，仅次于乌克兰。随后，他继续<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-ryder-joined-by-queens-roger-taylor-during-eurovision-performance-3443072">在 2023 年决赛中进行表演，并与女王鼓手罗杰·泰勒 (Roger Taylor) 一起登台表演</a>。</p><p>尽管因加沙战争期间<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eurovision-bosses-double-down-to-defend-decision-not-to-boycott-israel-over-gaza-war-3754132#:~:text=over%20Gaza%20war-,Eurovision%20bosses%20double%20down%20to%20defend%20decision,boycott%20Israel%20over%20Gaza%20war&amp;text=Eurovision%20organisers%20have%20defended%20their,over%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza.&amp;text=It%20comes%20ahead%20of%20the,this%20Saturday%20(May%2011).">以色列参加</a>今年的赛事而遭到抗议，但<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/despite-protests-eurovision-2024-breaks-global-viewing-figures-3759333">2024 年欧洲电视网的全球收视率仍打破了纪录</a>。根据<a href="https://www.ebu.ch/news/2024/05/eurovision-song-contest-2024-breaks-new-records-as-hundreds-of-millions-watch-and-listen-on-tv-and-digital-platforms">EBU 的数据</a>，共有 1.63 亿观众收看了包括总决赛在内的三场现场直播赛事。 </p><figure id="attachment_3756380" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3756380" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3756380" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OllyAlexander-Eurovision-2024-statement.jpg" alt="Olly Alexander 在 2024 年欧洲歌唱大赛舞台上现场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OllyAlexander-Eurovision-2024-statement.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OllyAlexander-Eurovision-2024-statement-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OllyAlexander-Eurovision-2024-statement-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OllyAlexander-Eurovision-2024-statement-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OllyAlexander-Eurovision-2024-statement-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OllyAlexander-Eurovision-2024-statement-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3756380" class="wp-caption-text"> Olly Alexander 在 2024 年欧洲歌唱大赛现场表演。图片来源：Martin Sylvest Andersen/Getty</figcaption></figure><p> Israel 的加入引发了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/hundreds-of-queer-artists-urge-olly-alexander-to-boycott-eurovision-2024-over-israels-participation-3610773">LGBT+ 群体对 Olly Alexander 的抵制呼吁，</a>超过 1,000 名瑞典艺术家也<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/robyn-fever-ray-first-aid-kit-among-1000-swedish-artists-calling-for-eurovision-to-ban-israel-3579906">呼吁今年禁止 Israel</a> ，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robyn">Robyn</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fever-ray">Fever Ray</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/first-aid-kit">First Aid Kit</a>等。超过<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/finnish-artists-sign-petition-calling-for-israel-to-be-banned-from-eurovision-3569080">1,400 名芬兰音乐界专业人士签署了一份请愿书，禁止该国参加这项比赛</a>。</p><p>以色列最终被允许参加比赛，并且由于政治中立条款，EBU 宣布他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eurovision-have-banned-palestinian-flags-and-symbols-3753455">保留移除巴勒斯坦旗帜和标志的权利</a>。他们后来继续<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/deleted-tiktok-reveals-moment-bambie-thug-was-forced-to-remove-pro-palestinian-message-its-fucked-up-3755454">审查爱尔兰选手 Bambie Thug，因为她在服装上隐藏了“停火”和“巴勒斯坦自由”字样</a>。</p><p>此外，今年的争议也随之而来，组织者在比赛前几个小时<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-netherlands-eurovision-entry-joost-klein-kicked-out-of-competition-3755424">取消了荷兰选手乔斯特·克莱因(Joost Klein)的参赛资格</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3611422" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3611422" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3611422" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/becky-hill-press-1.jpg" alt="贝基·希尔" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/becky-hill-press-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/becky-hill-press-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/becky-hill-press-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/becky-hill-press-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/becky-hill-press-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/becky-hill-press-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3611422" class="wp-caption-text">贝基·希尔.图片来源：Drapes SD</figcaption></figure><p>在贝基·希尔的其他新闻中，她的第二张录音室专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/becky-hill-tells-us-about-new-album-believe-me-now-im-not-the-underdog-anymore-3579114">《现在相信我吗？》</a>于今年早些时候发行，其中包括以<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/self-esteem">Self Esteem</a>为特色的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/becky-hill-and-self-esteem-tackle-sexual-assault-on-powerful-new-single-true-colours-3760088">强大单曲“True Colours”</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/becky-hill-tells-us-about-new-album-believe-me-now-im-not-the-underdog-anymore-3579114">与<em>NME</em>谈论“现在相信我吗？”今年早些时候</a>，希尔说：“我想搬进一个写着‘全球艺术家’而不是‘幸福的意外’的空间。跨越半个地球来到这里并让人们喜欢我的音乐，这让我觉得这一切都不是幻觉。”</p><p>她继续说道：“我觉得我终于摆脱了‘邻家女孩’的形象。我拼命地想坚持下去，因为我不想让任何人认为我太特别或者自以为是。</p><p> “我不想让人们问，‘贝基·希尔到底是谁？’但我已经成为了这个确切知道她是谁的人。我不需要贬低自己或自己的能力，因为我终于相信自己了。你可以在这张唱片上听到这一点。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/becky-hill-responds-to-bollocks-reports-shell-be-representing-uk-at-eurovision-2025-3807651">贝基·希尔 (Becky Hill) 对她将代表英国参加 2025 年欧洲电视网 (Eurovision 2025) 的“胡说八道”报道做出的回应</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
